’Ů@9bfc86fca13f26808df240a926a2c275694574fe7d98bcbc04be9fb8d284b22dÚŹTitle: title: du
Path: Flags
Content:
``--deref, -r``
: Dereference symlinks to their targets for size.
``--long, -l``
: Get underlying directories and files for each entry.
``--exclude, -x {glob}``
: Exclude these file names.
``--max-depth, -d {int}``
: Directory recursion limit.
``--min-size, -m {int}``
: Exclude files below this size.
``--all, -a``
: Include hidden files if '
*
' is provided.
